tip.text: Excellent breakfast buffet (sign up when checking in for a good discount.) Food always top quality & service fast & friendly. The beach is gorgeous & not at all crowded. Top resort in my book!
Finally, a good NY style bagel! Had lost faith in California bagels till now. Happiness!
Good, authentic Korean food at a great price. Prompt service too. I'm happy with my bibimbap.
Everyone here is skillful, sweet and helpful. You're in good hands whether you know exactly what you want or looking for a new look!
